Created directory: 0x03-sass_scss

Installed Node.js using NVM:
curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

Reopened terminal and installed Node v20.16:
nvm install 20.16

Attempted to install SASS version 3.7.4:
npm install sass -v 3.7.4
â†’ Error occurred: version not available

Resolved by installing latest SASS globally:
npm install -g sass

Verified installation:
sass --version
